latestPosts.caption:
From humble Beginnings as a CA to the visionary MAN behind @motilaloswalgroup🚀📈

With a net worth of $2.7 billion, according to @forbes, he has built a financial empire that boasts 11,000 employees and a 37-year presence in the market💸

Born in a Small village in Rajasthan, he came to Mumbai with BIG DREAMS 

Today, Motilal Oswal Financial Services Ltd, a company with a market capitalization of Rs. 32,058 Crores stands as a beacon of stability and growth for millions of Investors. 

He is None other than @mrmotilaloswal Sir. 

The most important thing I learnt from him: 

-NEVER Compromise on your ethics 
-Whatever you think, THINK BIG

In our podcast, @unstoppablewithsurbhi he shared valuable insights on:

✅How becoming a Chartered Accountant helped him in his Stock market Journey. 
✅Building a successful partnership with Mr Raamdeo Agrawal
✅Avoiding common mistakes as an early investor
✅The dark reality of insider trading
✅Creating a brand like the Motilal Oswal Group

What a Remarkable journey Determination and Resilience. 

It was an honour to meet Motilal Ostwal Sir, a true icon in the world of finance 

The Podcast is a perfect Sunday watch to inspire you in your Financial Journey. WATCH it Now. Link in Bio🚀

Finance, CA, CFA

CA’s are the backbone of India’s economy! Listen to what @sureshpprabhu sir, who is a Chartered Accountant himself and the former Minister for the Government has to say

Full Episode on my Youtube Channel

Watch to know how Chartered Accountants can drive nation development

It was great meeting @sureshpprabhu Sir, a CA and the former Union Minister of various portfolios, including Railways, Commerce & Industry, and Power.

I still remember meeting him for the first time when I was 15 years old - he was the Railway Minister back then, and I was thrilled to get his autograph! Fast forward 10 years, and I had the privilege of hosting him on my podcast: UNSTOPPABLE WITH SURBHI🚀

In our conversation, Suresh Prabhu sir shared why he made the unconventional switch from CA to politics. We also discussed some fascinating topics:

✅His most challenging portfolio: Which one did he find the toughest?

✅CA’s contribution to nation-building: How can Chartered Accountants make a meaningful impact?

✅India in the global market: What role can CA’s play in promoting India’s growth?

✅Leadership lessons from politics: What valuable insights did he gain from his experience?

Watch the entire podcast on my YOUTUBE CHANNEL to get inspired and motivated by Suresh Prabhu sir’s remarkable journey!
